works.complaint:
I have made several DMCA requests to Google to remove 

illegal URLs that
infringe on my copyright. I have noted that you have released my complaint
 
letters to Chilling Effects. They in turn have posted these letters on the
 
Internet, which violates my privacy.

I respectfully request that these letters be removed fortwith. I also  
request that any future DMCA complaints to Google not be forwarded to  
Chilling Effects. They have no business receiving them or posting them on 

the Internet, as this is a matter between me and Google only.
